data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath ranch located in a quiet, non HOA subdivision in Winder! Situated on a large level lot with a fenced in backyard. This home is move in ready, featuring a brand new roof and newer water heater. Offering LVP flooring throughout the main living areas and tons of natural light throughout. Kitchen offers white cabinets with a large eat-in breakfast area. Large flat backyard has a huge covered patio perfect for outdoor entertaining! Schedule your showing today!
